<HL>
   Children's Tapes Help the Sales Market Grow Up
   ----
   By Karen Blumenthal
   Staff Reporter of The Wall Street Journal
</HL>
<DATE>
12/24/91
</DATE>
<SO>
WALL STREET JOURNAL (J), PAGE B1
</SO>
<CO>
   DH DIS TWX
</CO>
<MS>
CONSUMER CYCLICAL (CYC)
</MS>
<IN>
